# Cron job configuration for NY Urban Ticket Tracker
# Add this line to your crontab (crontab -e on Linux/Mac)
# 
# For Windows, use Task Scheduler instead (see README.md)
#
# Run every 3 minutes (to avoid throttling the server):
# */3 * * * * cd /path/to/nyurban-ticket-tracker && /usr/bin/python3 check_availability.py >> availability.log 2>&1
#
# Or with virtual environment:
# */3 * * * * cd /path/to/nyurban-ticket-tracker && /path/to/venv/bin/python check_availability.py >> availability.log 2>&1
